#Initial Setup/Package installation 
```{r}
install.packages(c(
  "Seurat",
  "tidyverse",
  "patchwork",
  "pheatmap",
  "glmnet",
  "caret",
  "viridis"
))

if (!require("BiocManager"))
    install.packages("BiocManager")

BiocManager::install(c(
  "SingleCellExperiment",
  "GSVA",
  "clusterProfiler"
))
```
